Usage: alignObject [-help] [-mix] [-referToFirst] -side <side>

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-mix                   # consider all selected objects together. Or we will
                       # align obstrusts and other object seperately 
                       # (bool, optional)
-referToFirst          # refer to the first selected(NOT move the first object)
                       # (bool, optional)
-side <side>           # align to which side {left | right | center | top |
                       # bottom | middle} (string, required)